thread.title: Labrador Retriever still America's favorite, French Bulldog gets better spot

title: Labrador Retriever still America's favorite, French Bulldog gets better spot
text:
Labrador Retriever still America's favorite, French Bulldog gets better spot 3:33pm EDT - 00:54 
For the 27th consecutive year, the Labrador Retriever is America's most popular dog breed and the French Bulldog jumps two spots to come in at number four, according to the American Kennel Club said on Wednesday. Rough Cut
